    "body": "I guess @sarthak550 is having issues with `truffle migrate` which needs a network running at `http://localhost:8545`. Whereas, `truffle test` internally starts a Ganache network if there is no network specified in the `truffle-config.js`. If there is a `test` network specified in the `truffle-config.js`, then there should be a network running with that configuration.\r\n\r\nI hope this suggestion is helpful to you @joeax . Please do let us know if you still find this an issue.",
